headline.print_headline: Djokovic Wary of Raonic Threat in Paris
headline.main: Djokovic Wary of Raonic Threat in Paris

lead_paragraph: Having had a quiet start to his French Open campaign, Novak Djokovic can expect a tougher assignment on Tuesday when he faces up-and-coming Milos Raonic in the quarter-finals.
